== Support Vector Chef

This is my sandbox to learn more about Learning Machine.
It's using Support Vector Machine to understand if a recipe is comestible.

Lots of inspiration comes from igvita article
http://www.igvita.com/2008/01/07/support-vector-machines-svm-in-ruby/

And these slides
http://slidesha.re/98bXlB

And if you need more reference I suggest reading:
Programming Collective Intelligence http://oreilly.com/catalog/9780596529321


== Getting Started

bundle install
rake db:migrate
rake db:seed
rails server
open http://127.0.0.1:3000

teach it how to cook!